'''Ion Geant<U+0103>''' (born September 12, 1959) is a [[Romania]]n [[canoe racing|sprint canoer]] who competed from the late 1970s to the mid 1980s. Competing in two [[Summer Olympics]], he won a silver medal in the K-4 1000 m event at [[Moscow]] in [[1980 Summer Olympics|1980]].

